  "alternative_titles": "お隣の天使様にいつの間にか駄目人間にされていた件, The Angel Next Door Spoils Me Rotten, Tonari no Tenshi-sama ni Itsu no Ma ni ka Dame Ningen ni Sareteita Ken, She is the neighbor angel, I am spoilt by her.",
